Ranger Help for: make tools
============================

SYNTAX:      make tools
USAGE:       Wilderness
SLOT COST:   NA
BASE SP:     25
SKILL TYPE:  survival

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to prepare a reusable field kit from
wildcraft supplies. The Ranger needs 2 fieldstone, 1 flint, and
1 binding fiber. Fieldstone and flint come from mine or quarry, and
binding fiber comes from forage.

The field kit is stored in the Ranger's wildcraft pouch instead of
being carried as a fragile inventory item. It supports field survival
and mining work.
